          "description": "The clinic is  very clean , secure,  quiet,they have good team  work. The Staff, and  the  Admistration are professional\nThe Doctors ,The Nurses and the  pca taken  care good   all the patients  professionally I recommend  everyone to visit the Sydenham  clinic  264 west 118 street  Harlem. The clinic is one of the best clinic in New york city.",
