          "description": "Horrible service from front desk staff, nurses, doctors. specifically from the date 8/23/22 between 3-5:40 pm. Would not even recommend to my worst enemy. staff is unorganized, gentleman at front desk is rude, doctors like Mitchel don't do their work at all. If your looking to go in circles and argue, this is the place. A simple form for work, will get lost, told its not done, get told the doctor didn't do it, the social worker is on vacation, anpther assistant doctor wouldnt sign because he didmt personally see the patient.  Mind you all the informationfor the form were vaccines, blood work which was done and height and weight. if you've been there file a complaint against the health department. They're complaining about releasing Vaccination records but God forbid if that form would've been filed out and lost. Was also not given the supposedly supervisor's email \"Cesar\" because according to the nurse they don't have an email.",
